# comment-indented

## Input

```
  # indented comment
key value

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..31
  SPACE@0..2 "  "
  COMMENT@2..20
    SHARP@2..3 "#"
    SPACE@3..4 " "
    WORD@4..12 "indented"
    SPACE@12..13 " "
    WORD@13..20 "comment"
  NEWLINE@20..21 "\n"
  ENTRY@21..31
    WORD_KEY@21..24
      WORD@21..24 "key"
    SPACE@24..25 " "
    LINE_STRING@25..30
      STRING@25..30 "value"
    NEWLINE@30..31 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@21..24 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@25..30 "value",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

